narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: I learned about the history of and issues that exist within Southeast Asia. In addition, I developed my ability to analyze a culture within from an anthropological perspective.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: I think this course was great at creating an intimate learning environment for the students. I think it could have been improved by posing thought questions before the readings so we knew what points were important to focus on.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: This class is a great opportunity to learn about a unique region of the world and taught me about histories that I had previously taken for granted.
